title.narrative: Corporate Plan IV - Revenue to GDP ratio

Source: Targets are based on TRA's Revised 4th Corporate Plan (june 2015) and results are based on Tanzania National Bureau of Statistics (tax statistics report)
Note: The Corporate Plan 4 was revised after two years based on the GDP rebasing which affected the revenue to GDP ratio. TRA's vision was initially to increase revenue to GDP ratio to 19.9% which was revised to 13.9% by 2018. The Programme targets put forward have been revised in accordingly.
